mixin modal(jobDetail, modalId, modalTitle, btnType)
    div(class="modal fade" id=modalId data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
        tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby=modalId+'Label' aria-hidden="true"
    )
        div(class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered")
            div(class="modal-content")
                div(class="modal-header")
                    h5(class="modal-title" id=modalId+'Label') #{modalTitle}
                    button(type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal") 
                div(class="modal-body")
                    form(method="post"
                        action
                        form-action-cv
                        path=`/${prefixAdmin}/announce/${congTyId}` 
                    )
                        div(class="form-group")
                            label(for="HoTen") Họ tên 
                            input(type="text" class="form-control" id="HoTen" name="HoTen" value=jobDetail.infoUser.hoTen readonly)
                        div(class="form-group")
                            label(for="tenCV") Tên công việc
                            input(type="text" class="form-control" id="tenCV" name="tenCV" value=jobDetail.infoJob.tenCV readonly)
                        div(class="form-group")
                            label(for="thongBao") Lời nhắn
                            if(btnType=="accept")
                                textarea(name="thongBao" id="thongBao" class="form-control" required)
                            else 
                                textarea(name="thongBao" id="thongBao" class="form-control" required)
                                    | Thật tiếc nhưng chúng tôi thấy bạn chưa phù hợp với vị trí này!

                        button(
                            type="submit"
                            userId=jobDetail.userId 
                            maCV=jobDetail.maCV
                            class="btn btn-primary btn-large " 
                            button-submit
                        ) Gửi